<paragraph blockId="6.[151,1436,711,848]" pageId="6" pageNumber="64">
This species has its known distribution extending from the Caribbean to 
<collectingCountry box="[966,1080,711,735]" name="Argentina" pageId="6" pageNumber="64">Argentina</collectingCountry>
, and has some previous records from Minas Gerais (
<bibRefCitation author="Nieser, N. &amp; Melo, A. L." box="[377,612,749,773]" pageId="6" pageNumber="64" refId="ref7005" refString="Nieser, N. &amp; Melo, A. L. (1997) Os Heteropteros Aquaticos de Minas Gerais - Guia Introdutorio com Chave de Identificacao para as Especies de Nepomorpha e Gerromorpha. Editora UFMG, Belo Horizonte, 180 pp." type="book" year="1997">Nieser &amp; Melo 1997</bibRefCitation>
; 
<bibRefCitation author="Melo, A. L. &amp; Nieser, N." box="[624,859,749,773]" pageId="6" pageNumber="64" pagination="43 - 49" refId="ref6555" refString="Melo, A. L. &amp; Nieser, N. (2004) Faunistical notes on aquatic Heteroptera of Minas Gerais (Brazil): an annotated list of Gerromorpha and Nepomorpha collected near Januaria, MG. Lundiana, 5, 43 - 49." type="journal article" year="2004">Melo &amp; Nieser 2004</bibRefCitation>
). Its occurrence on Carmo do Rio Claro Municipality is herein reported for the first time.
</paragraph>
